<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="illustrate-vt">illustrate <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪləstreɪt/    美 /'ɪləstreɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>给…作插图：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an illustrated textbook
有插图的课本</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Over a hundred pictures and photos illustrate the book.
这本书有一百多幅插图和照片。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(用示例、图画等) 说明；解释：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>To illustrate my point</strong>, let me tell you a little story.
为了说明我的观点，我给你们讲个小故事吧。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>illustration /ˌɪlə'streɪʃn/ n [U] <br />
illustrator /'ɪləstreɪtə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>